            . I am a constable. I heard the cry of stop thief, ran out, and met the prisoner as he was running with the people.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180909-220-person1679">JAMES</persName>
             M'CULLOUGH. I am a watchman. I heard the alarm. I found the chain and seals on the ground.</p>
